article_id:3289,category_name:Updates,title_name:Regarding Additional Updates to the Kaleidoscape,image_path:,message:<div>The following additions were made to the Kaleidoscape on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1650866400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Additional Floors</div><div>・Floors 51 through 60 have been added and certain rewards have been adjusted.</div><div><br></div><div>■Additional Floor Skips</div><div>・Players may now skip to floor 35 or 40 once they have cleared that floor with any adventurer.</div><div><br></div><div>■Adventurer Level-Cap Increase</div><div>・The maximum adventurer level has been increased from 80 to 100.</div><div><br></div><div>■Additional Memories of the Sacred Tree</div><div>・New stories unlockable in Memories of the Sacred Tree have been added.</div><div><br></div><div>■Additional Treasure Trade Items</div><div>・New items have been added to the Treasure Trade.</div><div><br></div><div>■Additional Endeavors and Medals</div><div>・Kaleidoscape endeavors and medals for Notte&#39;s Notes have been added.</div><div><br></div><div>■Balance Adjustments</div><div>・Expanded the roster of bosses.</div><div><br></div><div>・Increased the amount of experience points earned for defeating a boss and when using the floor skip feature.</div><div><br></div><div>・Adjusted the HP of the boss who appears on floor 50. This update increased the adventurer level cap, meaning that players may be over-leveled by the time they reach the boss on floor 50 and easily defeat them as a result. We have increased the boss&#39;s HP to compensate.</div><div><br></div><div>Note: If you suspend a run before this update is applied and resume it afterward, you will not be able to progress to floors 51 through 60. In order to access these floors, please begin a new run of the Kaleidoscape after the update has been applied.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1650866400,update_time1650432325